text:
Guards, border guards and rescuers will be paid 10-15% more

05 Nov 2019, 13:29

Deputy Minister of Internal Affairs Anton Gerashchenko during the presentation of the state budget for 2020 said that the total budget of the security sector will amount to 93 billion UAH. That is, its funding will increase by 12.4%, the Facts say.
He added that the salaries of employees of the National Police will increase by 10%.
Salaries of employees will also increase:

State Border Service - by 15%;
State emergency services - by 14%;
National Guard - by 10%;
State Migration Service - by 6%.


